cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.GT. 

The paper deals with optimization in sponsored search auctions, which involves machine learning and decision-making. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves modeling the problem as a Markov Decision Process (MDP), which falls under cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
